{
  "video_id": "uTL9tm7S1Io",
  "title": "Your words may predict your future mental health | Mariano Sigman",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13006.0,
      "end_time": 18180.0,
      "text": "We have historical records that allow us to know how the ancient Greeks dressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18180.0,
      "end_time": 19458.0,
      "text": "how they lived,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19458.0,
      "end_time": 21004.0,
      "text": "how they fought ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21004.0,
      "end_time": 23432.0,
      "text": "but how did they think?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23432.0,
      "end_time": 27896.0,
      "text": "One natural idea is that the deepest aspects of human thought --"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27896.0,
      "end_time": 29792.0,
      "text": "our ability to imagine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29792.0,
      "end_time": 31213.0,
      "text": "to be conscious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31213.0,
      "end_time": 32468.0,
      "text": "to dream --"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32468.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34872.0,
      "text": "have always been the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34872.0,
      "end_time": 36395.0,
      "text": "Another possibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36395.0,
      "end_time": 40142.0,
      "text": "is that the social transformations that have shaped our culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40142.0,
      "end_time": 44911.0,
      "text": "may have also changed the structural columns of human thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44911.0,
      "end_time": 47459.0,
      "text": "We may all have different opinions about this."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47459.0,
      "end_time": 50644.0,
      "text": "Actually, it's a long-standing philosophical debate."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50644.0,
      "end_time": 54834.0,
      "text": "But is this question even amenable to science?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54834.0,
      "end_time": 57364.0,
      "text": "Here I'd like to propose"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57364.0,
      "end_time": 62160.0,
      "text": "that in the same way we can reconstruct how the ancient Greek cities looked"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62160.0,
      "end_time": 64572.0,
      "text": "just based on a few bricks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64572.0,
      "end_time": 68722.0,
      "text": "that the writings of a culture are the archaeological records,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68722.0,
      "end_time": 71905.0,
      "text": "the fossils, of human thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71905.0,
      "end_time": 73103.0,
      "text": "And in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73103.0,
      "end_time": 75333.0,
      "text": "doing some form of psychological analysis"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75333.0,
      "end_time": 78901.0,
      "text": "of some of the most ancient books of human culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78901.0,
      "end_time": 84880.0,
      "text": "Julian Jaynes came up in the '70s with a very wild and radical hypothesis:"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84880.0,
      "end_time": 87317.0,
      "text": "that only 3,000 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87317.0,
      "end_time": 93753.0,
      "text": "humans were what today we would call schizophrenics."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 93753.0,
      "end_time": 95285.0,
      "text": "And he made this claim"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95285.0,
      "end_time": 98610.0,
      "text": "based on the fact that the first humans described in these books"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 98610.0,
      "end_time": 100538.0,
      "text": "behaved consistently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100538.0,
      "end_time": 103578.0,
      "text": "in different traditions and in different places of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103578.0,
      "end_time": 107134.0,
      "text": "as if they were hearing and obeying voices"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107134.0,
      "end_time": 110198.0,
      "text": "that they perceived as coming from the Gods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110198.0,
      "end_time": 112063.0,
      "text": "or from the muses ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112063.0,
      "end_time": 115888.0,
      "text": "what today we would call hallucinations."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115888.0,
      "end_time": 118538.0,
      "text": "And only then, as time went on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118538.0,
      "end_time": 122213.0,
      "text": "they began to recognize that they were the creators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122213.0,
      "end_time": 125316.0,
      "text": "the owners of these inner voices."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125316.0,
      "end_time": 128055.0,
      "text": "And with this, they gained introspection:"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128055.0,
      "end_time": 131785.0,
      "text": "the ability to think about their own thoughts."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131785.0,
      "end_time": 135206.0,
      "text": "So Jaynes's theory is that consciousness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135206.0,
      "end_time": 138396.0,
      "text": "at least in the way we perceive it today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 138396.0,
      "end_time": 141960.0,
      "text": "where we feel that we are the pilots of our own existence --"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 141960.0,
      "end_time": 145456.0,
      "text": "is a quite recent cultural development."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145456.0,
      "end_time": 147266.0,
      "text": "And this theory is quite spectacular,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 147266.0,
      "end_time": 148723.0,
      "text": "but it has an obvious problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 148723.0,
      "end_time": 153085.0,
      "text": "which is that it's built on just a few and very specific examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 153085.0,
      "end_time": 154872.0,
      "text": "So the question is whether the theory"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 154872.0,
      "end_time": 159647.0,
      "text": "that introspection built up in human history only about 3,000 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159647.0,
      "end_time": 163543.0,
      "text": "can be examined in a quantitative and objective manner."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 163543.0,
      "end_time": 167130.0,
      "text": "And the problem of how to go about this is quite obvious."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 167130.0,
      "end_time": 170614.0,
      "text": "It's not like Plato woke up one day and then he wrote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 170614.0,
      "end_time": 172297.0,
      "text": "\"Hello, I'm Plato,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 172297.0,
      "end_time": 175210.0,
      "text": "and as of today, I have a fully introspective consciousness.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 175210.0,
      "end_time": 177527.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 177527.0,
      "end_time": 181467.0,
      "text": "And this tells us actually what is the essence of the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 181467.0,
      "end_time": 186434.0,
      "text": "We need to find the emergence of a concept that's never said."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 186434.0,
      "end_time": 190768.0,
      "text": "The word introspection does not appear a single time"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 190768.0,
      "end_time": 193728.0,
      "text": "in the books we want to analyze."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 193728.0,
      "end_time": 198571.0,
      "text": "So our way to solve this is to build the space of words."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 198571.0,
      "end_time": 201882.0,
      "text": "This is a huge space that contains all words"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201882.0,
      "end_time": 204708.0,
      "text": "in such a way that the distance between any two of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 204708.0,
      "end_time": 208460.0,
      "text": "is indicative of how closely related they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 208460.0,
      "end_time": 209635.0,
      "text": "So for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 209635.0,
      "end_time": 212556.0,
      "text": "you want the words \"dog\" and \"cat\" to be very close together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 212556.0,
      "end_time": 216809.0,
      "text": "but the words \"grapefruit\" and \"logarithm\" to be very far away."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 216809.0,
      "end_time": 221626.0,
      "text": "And this has to be true for any two words within the space."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 221626.0,
      "end_time": 224991.0,
      "text": "And there are different ways that we can construct the space of words."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 224991.0,
      "end_time": 226658.0,
      "text": "One is just asking the experts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 226658.0,
      "end_time": 228896.0,
      "text": "a bit like we do with dictionaries."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 228896.0,
      "end_time": 230348.0,
      "text": "Another possibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 230348.0,
      "end_time": 234087.0,
      "text": "is following the simple assumption that when two words are related,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 234087.0,
      "end_time": 236460.0,
      "text": "they tend to appear in the same sentences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 236460.0,
      "end_time": 237937.0,
      "text": "in the same paragraphs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 237937.0,
      "end_time": 239731.0,
      "text": "in the same documents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 239731.0,
      "end_time": 244231.0,
      "text": "more often than would be expected just by pure chance."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 244231.0,
      "end_time": 246305.0,
      "text": "And this simple hypothesis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 246305.0,
      "end_time": 247635.0,
      "text": "this simple method,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 247635.0,
      "end_time": 249266.0,
      "text": "with some computational tricks"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 249266.0,
      "end_time": 250679.0,
      "text": "that have to do with the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 250679.0,
      "end_time": 253767.0,
      "text": "that this is a very complex and high-dimensional space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 253767.0,
      "end_time": 256155.0,
      "text": "turns out to be quite effective."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 256154.99999999997,
      "end_time": 258980.99999999997,
      "text": "And just to give you a flavor of how well this works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 258981.0,
      "end_time": 263607.0,
      "text": "this is the result we get when we analyze this for some familiar words."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 263607.0,
      "end_time": 264816.0,
      "text": "And you can see first"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 264816.0,
      "end_time": 268118.0,
      "text": "that words automatically organize into semantic neighborhoods."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 268118.0,
      "end_time": 270359.0,
      "text": "So you get the fruits, the body parts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 270359.0,
      "end_time": 273119.0,
      "text": "the computer parts, the scientific terms and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 273119.0,
      "end_time": 277852.0,
      "text": "The algorithm also identifies that we organize concepts in a hierarchy."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 277852.0,
      "end_time": 279027.0,
      "text": "So for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 279027.0,
      "end_time": 282648.0,
      "text": "you can see that the scientific terms break down into two subcategories"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 282648.0,
      "end_time": 285338.0,
      "text": "of the astronomic and the physics terms."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 285338.0,
      "end_time": 287608.0,
      "text": "And then there are very fine things."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 287608.0,
      "end_time": 289537.0,
      "text": "For instance, the word astronomy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 289537.0,
      "end_time": 291376.0,
      "text": "which seems a bit bizarre where it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 291376.0,
      "end_time": 293448.0,
      "text": "is actually exactly where it should be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 293448.0,
      "end_time": 295067.0,
      "text": "between what it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 295067.0,
      "end_time": 296361.0,
      "text": "an actual science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 296361.0,
      "end_time": 297921.0,
      "text": "and between what it describes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 297921.0,
      "end_time": 300182.0,
      "text": "the astronomical terms."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 300182.0,
      "end_time": 302097.0,
      "text": "And we could go on and on with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 302097.0,
      "end_time": 304181.0,
      "text": "Actually, if you stare at this for a while,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 304181.0,
      "end_time": 306063.0,
      "text": "and you just build random trajectories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 306063.0,
      "end_time": 310018.0,
      "text": "you will see that it actually feels a bit like doing poetry."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 310018.0,
      "end_time": 311924.0,
      "text": "And this is because, in a way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 311924.0,
      "end_time": 316027.0,
      "text": "walking in this space is like walking in the mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 316027.0,
      "end_time": 317668.0,
      "text": "And the last thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 317668.0,
      "end_time": 321732.0,
      "text": "is that this algorithm also identifies what are our intuitions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 321732.0,
      "end_time": 325652.0,
      "text": "of which words should lead in the neighborhood of introspection."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 325652.0,
      "end_time": 326899.0,
      "text": "So for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 326899.0,
      "end_time": 330902.0,
      "text": "words such as \"self,\" \"guilt,\" \"reason,\" \"emotion,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 330902.0,
      "end_time": 332815.0,
      "text": "are very close to \"introspection,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 332815.0,
      "end_time": 333990.0,
      "text": "but other words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 333990.0,
      "end_time": 336181.0,
      "text": "such as \"red,\" \"football,\" \"candle,\" \"banana,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 336181.0,
      "end_time": 338054.0,
      "text": "are just very far away."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 338054.0,
      "end_time": 340840.0,
      "text": "And so once we've built the space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 340840.0,
      "end_time": 343690.0,
      "text": "the question of the history of introspection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 343690.0,
      "end_time": 346047.0,
      "text": "or of the history of any concept"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 346047.0,
      "end_time": 350850.0,
      "text": "which before could seem abstract and somehow vague,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 350850.0,
      "end_time": 352478.0,
      "text": "becomes concrete --"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 352478.0,
      "end_time": 356216.0,
      "text": "becomes amenable to quantitative science."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 356216.0,
      "end_time": 359002.0,
      "text": "All that we have to do is take the books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 359002.0,
      "end_time": 360407.0,
      "text": "we digitize them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 360407.0,
      "end_time": 363240.0,
      "text": "and we take this stream of words as a trajectory"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 363240.0,
      "end_time": 365233.0,
      "text": "and project them into the space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 365233.0,
      "end_time": 369011.0,
      "text": "and then we ask whether this trajectory spends significant time"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 369011.0,
      "end_time": 372760.0,
      "text": "circling closely to the concept of introspection."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 372760.0,
      "end_time": 373980.0,
      "text": "And with this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 373980.0,
      "end_time": 376116.0,
      "text": "we could analyze the history of introspection"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 376116.0,
      "end_time": 378061.0,
      "text": "in the ancient Greek tradition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 378061.0,
      "end_time": 381631.0,
      "text": "for which we have the best available written record."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 381631.0,
      "end_time": 383910.0,
      "text": "So what we did is we took all the books --"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 383910.0,
      "end_time": 386218.0,
      "text": "we just ordered them by time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 386218.0,
      "end_time": 387994.0,
      "text": "for each book we take the words"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 387994.0,
      "end_time": 389979.0,
      "text": "and we project them to the space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 389979.0,
      "end_time": 393035.0,
      "text": "and then we ask for each word how close it is to introspection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 393035.0,
      "end_time": 394590.0,
      "text": "and we just average that."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 394590.0,
      "end_time": 397812.0,
      "text": "And then we ask whether, as time goes on and on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 397812.0,
      "end_time": 401088.0,
      "text": "these books get closer, and closer and closer"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 401088.0,
      "end_time": 402866.0,
      "text": "to the concept of introspection."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 402866.0,
      "end_time": 407698.0,
      "text": "And this is exactly what happens in the ancient Greek tradition."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 407698.0,
      "end_time": 410849.0,
      "text": "So you can see that for the oldest books in the Homeric tradition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 410849.0,
      "end_time": 414285.0,
      "text": "there is a small increase with books getting closer to introspection."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 414285.0,
      "end_time": 416515.0,
      "text": "But about four centuries before Christ,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 416515.0,
      "end_time": 421247.0,
      "text": "this starts ramping up very rapidly to an almost five-fold increase"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 421247.0,
      "end_time": 423771.0,
      "text": "of books getting closer, and closer and closer"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 423771.0,
      "end_time": 426159.0,
      "text": "to the concept of introspection."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 426159.0,
      "end_time": 428607.0,
      "text": "And one of the nice things about this"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 428607.0,
      "end_time": 429829.0,
      "text": "is that now we can ask"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 429829.0,
      "end_time": 434962.0,
      "text": "whether this is also true in a different, independent tradition."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 434962.0,
      "end_time": 438162.0,
      "text": "So we just ran this same analysis on the Judeo-Christian tradition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 438162.0,
      "end_time": 441548.0,
      "text": "and we got virtually the same pattern."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 441548.0,
      "end_time": 446207.0,
      "text": "Again, you see a small increase for the oldest books in the Old Testament,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 446207.0,
      "end_time": 448145.0,
      "text": "and then it increases much more rapidly"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 448145.0,
      "end_time": 450008.0,
      "text": "in the new books of the New Testament."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 450008.0,
      "end_time": 452064.0,
      "text": "And then we get the peak of introspection"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 452064.0,
      "end_time": 454215.0,
      "text": "in \"The Confessions of Saint Augustine,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 454215.0,
      "end_time": 456897.0,
      "text": "about four centuries after Christ."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 456897.0,
      "end_time": 458865.0,
      "text": "And this was very important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 458865.0,
      "end_time": 462262.0,
      "text": "because Saint Augustine had been recognized by scholars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 462262.0,
      "end_time": 464458.0,
      "text": "philologists, historians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 464458.0,
      "end_time": 467060.0,
      "text": "as one of the founders of introspection."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 467060.0,
      "end_time": 471012.0,
      "text": "Actually, some believe him to be the father of modern psychology."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 471012.0,
      "end_time": 472875.0,
      "text": "So our algorithm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 472875.0,
      "end_time": 475741.0,
      "text": "which has the virtue of being quantitative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 475741.0,
      "end_time": 477028.0,
      "text": "of being objective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 477028.0,
      "end_time": 479068.0,
      "text": "and of course of being extremely fast --"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 479068.0,
      "end_time": 481489.0,
      "text": "it just runs in a fraction of a second --"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 481489.0,
      "end_time": 485016.0,
      "text": "can capture some of the most important conclusions"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 485016.0,
      "end_time": 488317.0,
      "text": "of this long tradition of investigation."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 488317.0,
      "end_time": 491992.0,
      "text": "And this is in a way one of the beauties of science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 491992.0,
      "end_time": 495492.0,
      "text": "which is that now this idea can be translated"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 495492.0,
      "end_time": 498769.0,
      "text": "and generalized to a whole lot of different domains."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 498769.0,
      "end_time": 503560.0,
      "text": "So in the same way that we asked about the past of human consciousness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 503560.0,
      "end_time": 506990.0,
      "text": "maybe the most challenging question we can pose to ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 506990.0,
      "end_time": 511550.0,
      "text": "is whether this can tell us something about the future of our own consciousness."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 511550.0,
      "end_time": 513044.0,
      "text": "To put it more precisely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 513044.0,
      "end_time": 515484.0,
      "text": "whether the words we say today"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 515484.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520705.00000000006,
      "text": "can tell us something of where our minds will be in a few days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 520705.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521880.00000000006,
      "text": "in a few months"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 521880.0,
      "end_time": 523597.0,
      "text": "or a few years from now."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 523597.0,
      "end_time": 526641.0,
      "text": "And in the same way many of us are now wearing sensors"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 526641.0,
      "end_time": 528451.0,
      "text": "that detect our heart rate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 528451.0,
      "end_time": 529744.0,
      "text": "our respiration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 529744.0,
      "end_time": 531435.0,
      "text": "our genes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 531435.0,
      "end_time": 535110.0,
      "text": "on the hopes that this may help us prevent diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 535110.0,
      "end_time": 538655.0,
      "text": "we can ask whether monitoring and analyzing the words we speak,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 538655.0,
      "end_time": 541362.0,
      "text": "we tweet, we email, we write,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 541362.0,
      "end_time": 547087.0,
      "text": "can tell us ahead of time whether something may go wrong with our minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 547087.0,
      "end_time": 548645.0,
      "text": "And with Guillermo Cecchi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 548645.0,
      "end_time": 551670.0,
      "text": "who has been my brother in this adventure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 551670.0,
      "end_time": 554228.0,
      "text": "we took on this task."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 554228.0,
      "end_time": 559784.0,
      "text": "And we did so by analyzing the recorded speech of 34 young people"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 559784.0,
      "end_time": 563434.0,
      "text": "who were at a high risk of developing schizophrenia."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 563434.0,
      "end_time": 566339.0,
      "text": "And so what we did is, we measured speech at day one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 566339.0,
      "end_time": 569605.0,
      "text": "and then we asked whether the properties of the speech could predict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 569605.0,
      "end_time": 572125.0,
      "text": "within a window of almost three years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 572125.0,
      "end_time": 575427.0,
      "text": "the future development of psychosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 575427.0,
      "end_time": 577817.0,
      "text": "But despite our hopes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 577817.0,
      "end_time": 581793.0,
      "text": "we got failure after failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 581793.0,
      "end_time": 585699.0,
      "text": "There was just not enough information in semantics"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 585699.0,
      "end_time": 588516.0,
      "text": "to predict the future organization of the mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 588516.0,
      "end_time": 590349.0,
      "text": "It was good enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 590349.0,
      "end_time": 594548.0,
      "text": "to distinguish between a group of schizophrenics and a control group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 594548.0,
      "end_time": 597284.0,
      "text": "a bit like we had done for the ancient texts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 597284.0,
      "end_time": 601164.0,
      "text": "but not to predict the future onset of psychosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 601164.0,
      "end_time": 602894.0,
      "text": "But then we realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 602894.0,
      "end_time": 607006.0,
      "text": "that maybe the most important thing was not so much what they were saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 607006.0,
      "end_time": 609679.0,
      "text": "but how they were saying it."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 609679.0,
      "end_time": 610923.0,
      "text": "More specifically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 610923.0,
      "end_time": 613774.0,
      "text": "it was not in which semantic neighborhoods the words were,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 613774.0,
      "end_time": 616398.0,
      "text": "but how far and fast they jumped"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 616398.0,
      "end_time": 619247.0,
      "text": "from one semantic neighborhood to the other one."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 619247.0,
      "end_time": 621002.0,
      "text": "And so we came up with this measure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 621002.0,
      "end_time": 623415.0,
      "text": "which we termed semantic coherence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 623415.0,
      "end_time": 628243.0,
      "text": "which essentially measures the persistence of speech within one semantic topic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 628243.0,
      "end_time": 631294.0,
      "text": "within one semantic category."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 631294.0,
      "end_time": 635365.0,
      "text": "And it turned out to be that for this group of 34 people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 635365.0,
      "end_time": 639048.0,
      "text": "the algorithm based on semantic coherence could predict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 639048.0,
      "end_time": 641572.0,
      "text": "with 100 percent accuracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 641572.0,
      "end_time": 644976.0,
      "text": "who developed psychosis and who will not."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 644976.0,
      "end_time": 647937.0,
      "text": "And this was something that could not be achieved --"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 647937.0,
      "end_time": 649469.0,
      "text": "not even close --"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 649469.0,
      "end_time": 654525.0,
      "text": "with all the other existing clinical measures."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 654525.0,
      "end_time": 658128.0,
      "text": "And I remember vividly, while I was working on this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 658128.0,
      "end_time": 660469.0,
      "text": "I was sitting at my computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 660469.0,
      "end_time": 663128.0,
      "text": "and I saw a bunch of tweets by Polo --"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 663128.0,
      "end_time": 666319.0,
      "text": "Polo had been my first student back in Buenos Aires,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 666319.0,
      "end_time": 668413.0,
      "text": "and at the time he was living in New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 668413.0,
      "end_time": 670525.0,
      "text": "And there was something in this tweets --"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 670525.0,
      "end_time": 674050.0,
      "text": "I could not tell exactly what because nothing was said explicitly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 674050.0,
      "end_time": 676095.0,
      "text": "but I got this strong hunch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 676095.0,
      "end_time": 680347.0,
      "text": "this strong intuition, that something was going wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 680347.0,
      "end_time": 683094.0,
      "text": "So I picked up the phone, and I called Polo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 683094.0,
      "end_time": 685362.0,
      "text": "and in fact he was not feeling well."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 685362.0,
      "end_time": 687323.0,
      "text": "And this simple fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 687323.0,
      "end_time": 689838.0,
      "text": "that reading in between the lines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 689838.0,
      "end_time": 694124.0,
      "text": "I could sense, through words, his feelings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 694124.0,
      "end_time": 697987.0,
      "text": "was a simple, but very effective way to help."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 697987.0,
      "end_time": 699649.0,
      "text": "What I tell you today"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 699649.0,
      "end_time": 702181.0,
      "text": "is that we're getting close to understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 702181.0,
      "end_time": 706491.0,
      "text": "how we can convert this intuition that we all have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 706491.0,
      "end_time": 707880.0,
      "text": "that we all share,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 707880.0,
      "end_time": 710102.0,
      "text": "into an algorithm."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 710102.0,
      "end_time": 711587.0,
      "text": "And in doing so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 711587.0,
      "end_time": 716261.0,
      "text": "we may be seeing in the future a very different form of mental health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 716261.0,
      "end_time": 721906.0,
      "text": "based on objective, quantitative and automated analysis"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 721906.0,
      "end_time": 723639.0,
      "text": "of the words we write,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 723639.0,
      "end_time": 725200.0,
      "text": "of the words we say."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 725200.0,
      "end_time": 726375.0,
      "text": "Gracias."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 726375.0,
      "end_time": 736375.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}